items.title: CatDog Wiki
items.headline: Trot over to the CatDog Wiki!
items.desc:
CatDog was a Nickelodeon television series focusing on the life of a cat-dog hybrid, their friends, and their enemies. The show was cancelled on June 15, 2005 , though it is still playing in reruns on TeenNick.

The series depicts the life of conjoined brothers, with one half being a Cat and the other a Dog.

items.headline: Erin Hunter's Survivor Dogs Wiki
items.desc: A fan of Erin Hunter's newest series, Survivors? This wiki is all about it! Read about the first book, that came out August 21, learn about the characters, and more! The more editors, the better! Create Fan-art and post it on the wiki for the rest of the wiki to see! What's more, there will be a contest held for the best Fan-art! So come on down to the Survivor Dogs Wiki, and maybe meet some other Survivors fans too!

items.name: Poochpedia
items.title: Poochpedia
items.headline: See the Poochpedia Wiki!!
items.desc:
Our wiki is entirely devoted to dogs, man's best friend. Here on Poochpedia, we create pages on dog breeds, dog food brands, training, movies, etc. Find information on various different dog breeds, including their origin, temperament, and more! Learn how to train your pooch with our helpful training guidelines. Find which dog food brand is right for your pup! There is so much info on Poochpedia, we don't know what to do with it! Love dogs? Then this is the right wiki for you.

Be aware that this is still a work-in-progress. So come on!
